title: Year End Bonus Episode
description: Sean and Dr. Wali reflect on a year of celebrity ailments, share listener stories, and answer listener questions. And for the first time ever, the Dr. Wali vs. Sean Smackdown in Dr. Wali’s Hall of Fame trivia game.
